      <title>肯尼亚放弃了8亿美元的IMF评论，寻求新计划</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-03-17/kenya-seeks-new-imf-program-after-failing-to-secure-800-million</link>
      <description><![CDATA[肯尼亚同意不对现有设施的最终审查进行最终审查后，要求国际货币基金一项新的资金计划，该设施将解锁8亿美元。东非国家的纽带跌倒了。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-03-17/kenya-seeks-new-imf-program-after-failing-to-secure-800-million</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 17 Mar 2025 06:20:29 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>股票随着零售销量弱而上升，但并不糟糕：市场包装</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-03-16/asia-to-extend-stock-rally-on-new-chinese-measures-markets-wrap</link>
      <description><![CDATA[华尔街交易员担心所有关税剧在混合零售销售中获得了一定程度的减免，而股票的股票则减轻，而股票上涨和短期债券，因此对消费者支出的回调更大。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-03-16/asia-to-extend-stock-rally-on-new-chinese-measures-markets-wrap</guid>
      <pubDate>Sun, 16 Mar 2025 22:27:31 GMT</pubDate>
